      <title>葡萄牙极右翼政党希望利用抗议投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/portugal-election-2024-far-right-chega-may-capitalize-on-voter-anger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总理安东尼奥·科斯塔突然辞职后，葡萄牙将于本周末举行选举，这让选民有机会要么坚持社会党，要么选择变革并加入整个欧洲的右倾趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/portugal-election-2024-far-right-chega-may-capitalize-on-voter-anger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
