    <item>
      <title>印度反对派称，如果莫迪没有获得多数票，他将面临“潘多拉魔盒”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/modi-faces-pandora-s-box-if-no-majority-india-opposition-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在即将宣布的选举之前，印度反对派联盟在民意调查中远远落后。一位重要成员警告称，如果执政党赢得最多席位但未能在议会中获得多数席位，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪将面临麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/modi-faces-pandora-s-box-if-no-majority-india-opposition-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍明在加州众议院波特席位竞选中取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/baugh-min-advance-in-california-house-race-for-porter-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美联社报道，共和党人斯科特·鲍（Scott Baugh）和民主党人戴夫·明（Dave Min）是加州第 47 国会选区初选中得票最多的两名候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/baugh-min-advance-in-california-house-race-for-porter-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港拟在新国安法中对犯罪行为判处无期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/hk-publishes-article-23-draft-as-it-fast-tracks-new-security-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港在一项安全措施草案中提议对与叛国和叛乱有关的罪行判处无期徒刑，官员们正在寻求快速立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/hk-publishes-article-23-draft-as-it-fast-tracks-new-security-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 00:25:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在国情咨文中启动2024年竞选，瞄准特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/biden-speech-to-cast-trump-as-bent-on-revenge-and-retribution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登试图为他与唐纳德·特朗普的连任再战注入新的活力，他发表了一场充满活力且尖锐的政治性国情咨文演讲，与共和党人发生争执，并针对了一个他从未透露姓名的对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/biden-speech-to-cast-trump-as-bent-on-revenge-and-retribution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 23:07:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
